{"tid":1619051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個post一定要置頂，睇緊記者會直播嘅全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-10-04T07:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:57:46.000Z","uid":254923,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83703e7184da9e4e136fd5bc830135d565a1a4ea","tid":1619051,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:15:29.000Z","msg":"唔好留言屌鳩佢，咁樣做係毫無幫助<br />\n我哋應該要留言宣傳我哋下一步嘅行動<br />\n大家可以試吓咁樣留言，等更加多嘅人可以響應我哋嘅下一步行動<br />\n<br />\n重點戰場： RTHK，立場，蘋果，東網，有線<br />\n<br />\n人海戰術啊，絕對會影響今晚嘅行動<br />\n大家一定要咁樣留言，佢呢個方向都得<br />\n<br />\n1.幪面法只係第一步，如果大家咁樣驚嘅話，我哋就注定會輸，各位今晚見<br />\n<br />\n2. 五大訴求缺一不可，各位今晚見<br />\n<br />\n3. 政府依然選擇用警察解決政治問題，我哋唯有今晚見<br />\n<br />\n4. 惡法將會陸續有嚟，我哋今晚見，傳開去！<br />\n<br />\n我要係所有直播平台見到呢啲，咁樣屌鳩佢哋係冇用架！"},{"pid":"1640de349c27a2312eb1227a63be4d008edefa9f","tid":1619051,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"簡簡單單一句：今晚見，光復香港 時代革命<br />\n唔好掛住屌鳩佢哋啊<br />\n我哋要好好利用呢次直播"},{"pid":"d4e5d001bfebcb607dd40340f36cc14ea132296a","tid":1619051,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:17:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c6c0560cd1d5e2e57a43fc1fc0cbb5be9cb416","tid":1619051,"uid":267311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:17:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f99ead0b67e7db965e3446395fe9ad6debf156","tid":1619051,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fdc666bf5207281fc0f5ac312bdbc036623ebd47","tid":1619051,"uid":322637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d587ea8d7f9478ab074bb8e812773da75787e424","tid":1619051,"uid":25492